🛠️ Task 5 – Job Outputs

Add an output to the build job:

  build:
    needs: test
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    outputs:
      build_status: ${{ steps.build-step.outputs.status }}

    steps:
      - name: Checkout Code
        uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Build Application
        id: build-step
        run: |
          mkdir -p build
          echo "Build completed" > build/result.txt
          echo "status=success" >> "$GITHUB_OUTPUT"

A job can pass information to another job using outputs.

🛠️ Task 6 – Add a Deployment Simulation

Add:

  deploy:
    name: Deploy Application
    needs: build
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    environment: production

    steps:
      - name: Download Artifact
        uses: actions/download-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: application-build
          path: build/

      - name: Deploy
        run: |
          echo "Deploying application..."
          ls -la build/
          echo "Deployment completed successfully"

