🔥 Production Problem to Solve
Problem

Your pipeline shows:

build job skipped

But your test job succeeded.

Investigate:

Check the needs relationship.
Check whether the job name is correct.
Check whether an earlier dependency failed.
Check the workflow execution graph.
Check whether a condition prevented execution.

Example:

needs: test

The job name must exactly match:

test:
